cropit
------

Crops and resizes images.

Dependencies
------------

To build, one needs to install the following Debian packages. There should be 
similar names for each of those on other operating systems.

 * libcv-dev
 * libcvaux-dev
 * libhighgui-dev
 * libboost-program-options-dev
 * libboost-filesystem-dev
 * libboost-system-dev

